# Tech Stack and Configuration

This project uses TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, and shadcn/ui for development.

## TypeScript Configuration
- Main configuration in [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json)
- App-specific configuration in [tsconfig.app.json](mdc:tsconfig.app.json)
- Node-specific configuration in [tsconfig.node.json](mdc:tsconfig.node.json)

## Tailwind CSS
- Configuration is integrated with shadcn/ui
- Styles are defined in [src/index.css](mdc:src/index.css)
- Uses the "new-york" style theme
- CSS variables are enabled for theming

## shadcn/ui
- Configuration in [components.json](mdc:components.json)
- Components are located in `@/components`
- Utilities are in `@/lib/utils`
- Uses Lucide as the icon library
- Follows the shadcn/ui component structure:
  - UI components in `@/components/ui`
  - Custom components in `@/components`

## Important Notes:
- Always use TypeScript for new files
- Follow shadcn/ui's component patterns
- Use Tailwind classes for styling
- Maintain type safety throughout the codebase
- Use the provided path aliases (e.g., `@/components`, `@/lib`)
